        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Minimize expenses by batching requests where possible to reduce call counts. Cache frequent OCR results using a key based on image hashes to avoid redundant processing. Monitor usage via the dashboard to identify peak periods and adjust scaling policies. Consider implementing client-side image compression to reduce payload sizes and processing time, directly impacting costs."
