        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For high-throughput scenarios, leverage asynchronous processing with webhook callbacks to handle large volumes without blocking threads. Set appropriate timeout values (e.g., 30 seconds) and use connection pooling for efficient resource management. Test with varied image qualities to calibrate confidence thresholds, balancing accuracy against computational overhead. Scale horizontally by distributing calls across multiple API keys if permitted by your plan."
